description:
Danny and comedian Chloe Fineman chat about Oprah and Reese Witherspoon's friendship, diet fads, celebrity Instagram accounts, #RHOA, and SO much more. Dr. Heavenly from Bravo's Married to Medicine also calls in to recap the iconic reunion.
